[Memphis Pro Extra Bold](http://web.archive.org/web/20131017074535/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/memphis/). Rudolf Wolf designed Memphis for Stempel in 1929. Digital Memphis published by Linotype and Adobe. Also Geometric Slabserif 703 by Bitstream.
